。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外有用戶在 Reddit 討論區回報 PS5 經常無故出現「資料庫已損壞」的訊息，有用戶建議不同解決方法：PS5 應盡快升級系統軟件，並確保沒有任何下載，並重新啟動主機嘗試解決問題，如果問題仍存在，需要透過回復出廠設定來解決此問題。<br />\n<br />\n最後還有一位用戶在 Twitter 上回報了儲存裝置重建時出現錯誤的問題，<strong><span class=\"red\">他懷疑原因是使用了外置式儲存裝置</span></strong>，他正將此事反映給 Sony 尋求解決方法。"},{"pid":"c77d12145cbf1535aad5bd51b943dbd9f53b6412","tid":2286763,"uid":166032,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7f8b1475f45b6ea1bf4e1630d2eaab0a56904886","tid":2286763,"uid":38904,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T09:03:38.000Z","msg":"不朽都話買第1水都係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"你買手提電話記得叉夠24粒鐘先好用，用剩10%先叉電<br />\n<br />\n還是你個年代未有手提電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26cb34dabd90d0453700c46c1fa4bdab0cef143","tid":2286763,"uid":59499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"大家記得有貨都唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持大家唔好買、又大部又垃圾"},{"pid":"7652edb065b5fd78de5935e19e7fc0fb85f84204","tid":2286763,"uid":200328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5cfb5ebea38ef84996879d869e010bd124000db8","tid":2286763,"uid":10504,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"之前無意中 睇到某youtuber直播試機 <br />\n個傻閪話 ps5因為機能咁勁先咁大部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nxbx機能夠勁啦 點解人地整到咁細但畫面又得做好過你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心sony曬錢請埋D濕9 youtuber 不能搞好部機啦 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"Sony啲錢俾撚晒去請人做媒洗10分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正經野就on99咁"},{"pid":"3d40fddaea11c0d7440cae5fc6e284262cfb0196","tid":2286763,"uid":21282,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:27:02.000